  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 6 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf 59 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A 59-year-old man has been arrested for abusing a 6-year-old girl who was playing in the yard",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna. Police have arrested a 59-year-old man for abusing a 6-year-old girl in the area under the Ilavalai police division.",
        "The victim's mother was told by a neighbor that the girl's mother had taken her into a room and abused her while she was attending an event.",
        "The suspect has been arrested following a complaint lodged by his mother with the police in this regard.",
        "The man who took the girl's mouth in the courtyard of the girl who was playing in the courtyard has taken steps to appear in court as the young police said that the girl had abused the girl."
      ],
